MCP-first capture flow validated. SessionStart hook now injects RULE 0 at top of guidance, instructing to call mcp__subcog__memory.capture BEFORE outputting visual blocks. This ensures blocks have full URN with ID, which Stop hook recognizes as already-saved and skips.